1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 6=

16
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:54,206
(Ms. Bai Liangliang's work is suspended starting today.)

17
00:01:54,206 --> 00:01:58,580
(Ms. Chen Xi will temporarily oversee Investment Dept 1.)

18
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,719
Muran,

19
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,680
are you with Mr. Jiang?

20
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,400
Did you tell him?

21
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,680
I haven't found the right opportunity.

22
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,159
You know,

23
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,639
I can't leave right now.

24
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,800
I know.

25
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,880
If I get the chance, I'll definitely
put in a good word for you.

26
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,879
Liangliang,

27
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,159
I'm here.

28
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,599
I know you got into trouble.

29
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,800
I was so worried.

30
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,240
What are you worried about?

31
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,000
You look quite happy to me.

32
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:43,680
Liangliang.

33
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,759
Dear,

34
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,439
given our relationship,

35
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,560
you'd be more at ease

36
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,400
with me taking over, wouldn't you?

37
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,479
Who said I have to leave?

38
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,599
You're certainly in a hurry.

39
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:58,840
My dear,

40
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:01,240
I'm not in a hurry at all.

41
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,439
Look,

42
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,840
the HR notice

43
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,000
made it very clear.

44
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,400
You

45
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,439
are only suspended from work.

46
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,759
And I

47
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,560
am only temporarily in charge of Dept 1.

48
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,039
I think

49
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:16,240
you should just go
and take a nice vacation.

50
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,919
As the caretaker for Dept. 1,

51
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,680
I'll take care of this for you.

52
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,759
Do you have something to say to me?

53
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:49,639
If I said

54
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:51,639
I hope you'll leave Lysen voluntarily,

55
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:54,159
would you be willing?

56
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,599
Will my leaving

57
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,599
solve the problem?

58
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,800
Mr. Jiang has always followed
one hiring principle,

59
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,000
which is safety.

60
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,680
Right now at Lysen,

61
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:09,000
every project we handle
is worth hundreds of millions.

62
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,000
If a person isn't "safe",

63
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:13,199
it means Lysen
is exposed to risk everywhere.

64
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,520
You think we don't know

65
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:17,170
that Bai Liangliang's
breakdown yesterday

66
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,720
was your plan?

67
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,480
What I planned

68
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,439
doesn't matter

69
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:27,360
to Mr. Jiang.

70
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,040
What matters

71
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,879
is what Mr. Jiang

72
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,959
has planned for Lysen.

73
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:36,600
Lysen has already
completed its initial accumulation.

74
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:38,240
Mr. Jiang is going to take Lysen

75
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,160
to a whole new height.

76
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:42,990
Going against the current,
if you don't advance, you fall back.

77
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:45,199
Failing to move forward
is a predicament.

78
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,839
Lysen isn't in a predicament.

79
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:47,720
But Mr. Jiang needs

80
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,199
newcomers like us to enter the field.

81
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,040
Rao Yuci,

82
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,279
it's working hours,

83
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:54,160
so why aren't you at your desk
instead of wandering around?

84
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:54,920
Yu Peidong,

85
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,160
where are your manners?

86
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:58,839
What's wrong?

87
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:00,040
I knocked before coming in.

88
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,199
I need to take my employee back.

89
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:04,079
Time to work.

90
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,340
Don't stop us from making money.

91
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,360
Let's go.

92
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,720
Go on.

93
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,879
Say bye-bye to Ms. Ren.

94
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:18,680
Bye-bye.

95
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,879
Mr. Jiang, you heard everything.

96
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,759
Interesting.

97
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,399
I really think

98
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,720
you should reconsider.

99
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,439
This Rao Yuci

100
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,639
is truly very dangerous.

101
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:44,399
I don't think

102
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,160
she's who you think she is.

103
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:49,839
Then, who do I think she is?

104
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,279
Back then,

105
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,920
when I appointed Bai Liangliang,

106
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,000
you were also worried.

107
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:56,319
You really underestimated
a person's ambition.

108
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,519
Ren Jing,

109
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,839
don't try to guess anyone's mind.

110
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:03,160
You can't even predict the market,

111
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,360
let alone the human heart.

112
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,360
Hello, you're looking
for Director Wu, right?

113
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,000
Yes.

114
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,759
Were you okay last night?

115
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,480
I'm fine.

116
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,439
The whole company is saying

117
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,240
that yesterday,

118
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:27,920
you drove Bai Liangliang crazy.

119
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,120
Mr. Yu.

120
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,079
What?

121
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,959
No, nothing.

122
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:36,600
What's the next plan?

123
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,800
Mr. Yu, weren't you

124
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,439
uninterested in these things?

125
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,959
I've always been interested in
punishing evil and promoting good.

126
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:49,160
And I thought about

127
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,519
those things you said to me

128
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,839
in the office that day.

129
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,480
They actually make a lot of sense.

130
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,959
Mr. Yu, I didn't mean to make you
help me deal with Bai Liangliang.

131
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,279
But look at

132
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,519
the current state of Dept 3.

133
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,600
If we don't have some ambition,

134
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,839
Lysen will weed us out soon.

135
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,279
So,

136
00:07:04,839 --> 00:07:05,759
just like me,

137
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,970
climbing up is the only way
to get a chance.

138
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:19,560
Next time there's something
to take down Bai Liangliang,

139
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,040
call me. I'll cooperate.

140
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,240
We'll have a secret signal.

141
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:24,879
For example,

142
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,759
"Yu Peidong,

143
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,920
you're a total idiot."

144
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,380
I'll understand as soon as I hear it.

145
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:37,040
How is it?

146
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,600
Did I ever have

147
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,079
any unpleasantness with you, Ms. Ren?

148
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,839
There's never been
any unpleasantness between us.

149
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,360
Mr. Jiang only asked me to take a leave,

150
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,120
not to resign.

151
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,720
And you

152
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,279
let Chen Xi oversee Dept 1 so quickly.

153
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,000
What does this mean?

154
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,959
This email

155
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,439
was cc'd to the whole company.

156
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,319
How do you know

157
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:00,560
it wasn't Mr. Jiang's idea?

158
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,120
Besides,

159
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,199
Dept 1

160
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:05,319
has hundreds of
investment reports to process daily.

161
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,839
The pressure is indeed quite high.

162
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,839
Distributing some of that to Dept 2

163
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:10,100
isn't hard to understand, right?

164
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,160
If you all just focused on your work,

165
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,079
then Mr. Jiang

166
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,680
wouldn't have such a headache.

167
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,800
What do you mean by that, Ms. Ren?

168
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:27,959
That day at the observation deck,

169
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,079
you were so certain

170
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:30,879
that there was a knife in Rao Yuci's bag.

171
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,399
Who told you that?

172
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,240
Liangliang,

173
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,159
Lysen

174
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,639
isn't your personal playground.

175
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,840
You need to know

176
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,559
who you are.

177
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:54,820
(Caution Wet Floor)

178
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,080
Get out.

179
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,240
Get out!

180
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,519
Mr. Jiang,

181
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,440
your golf game
is getting better and better.

182
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,370
You must have been
practicing a lot lately.

183
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:25,279
Compared to people like you
who have played since childhood,

184
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:26,360
I still can't compete.

185
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,759
How has Ms. Bai been lately?

186
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:30,840
She's fine.

187
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,120
She even asked me to send her regards.

188
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,960
I'm quite ashamed.

189
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,919
I should have visited her sooner.

190
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:40,039
The Southeast Asian project

191
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:41,679
owed much to her guidance.

192
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,080
You did a good job too.

193
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,399
Tell me,

194
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:45,320
what do you want?

195
00:09:45,610 --> 00:09:47,279
I can't let
your hard work go unrewarded.

196
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:48,840
Besides,

197
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,519
it would be hard to explain

198
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:52,279
to Ms. Bai otherwise.

199
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:57,799
I heard about Liangliang.

200
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:03,080
Pleading for your girlfriend?

201
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,519
No.

202
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,960
You misunderstood.

203
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,519
I'm not here to plead for her.

204
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,679
On the contrary,

205
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,639
I think your handling of it was very fair.

206
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,000
Liangliang was in charge
of Dept 1 alone.

207
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,500
The pressure
on her shoulders was too much.

208
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,960
You gave her time off,
so I should be thanking you instead.

209
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,440
Of course, you also know

210
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,280
that once the position
in Dept 1 is vacant,

211
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:27,430
certain people in the company
will definitely have other ideas.

212
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,600
I know you

213
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,000
have your own thoughts

214
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,200
on that position in Dept 1.

215
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,440
Before you

216
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,919
finalize the personnel,

217
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:36,360
you can always come to me.

218
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:49,860
(Liuxiang Old Jiangxi Rice Noodles)

219
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:05,480
Yuci,

220
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,720
come on in.

221
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:08,440
Come, have a seat.

222
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:14,399
I saved this especially for you.

223
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:17,159
Boss, two more orders
of fried rice noodles.

224
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:18,360
Okay.

225
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,799
Thank you.

226
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,120
Yuci, have you ever had Jiangxi cuisine?

227
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,399
No.

228
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:27,399
This is stir-fried
cured pork with mugwort.

229
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:30,440
This is a white sugar sponge cake.

230
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,350
These are pickled bamboo shoots.

231
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,639
The most

232
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:36,799
authentic dish here
is the Nanchang fried rice noodles.

233
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,240
You should try some in a bit.

234
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,110
Here's yours. Careful, it's hot.

235
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,440
Okay, thank you.

236
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:55,960
It's delicious.

237
00:11:58,639 --> 00:11:59,440
I remember

238
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:01,120
when I was studying in New York,

239
00:12:01,770 --> 00:12:03,159
I really craved these rice noodles.

240
00:12:03,399 --> 00:12:05,480
But I couldn't buy
authentic Nanchang rice noodles.

241
00:12:06,879 --> 00:12:07,960
So my ex-wife and I

242
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,000
set up a stone mill

243
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:10,759
to grind rice milk ourselves

244
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:12,120
and make rice noodles,

245
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:13,960
just for this specific taste.

246
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:30,799
Sorry, Ms. Bai,

247
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,720
I'm late.

248
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:33,039
I haven't been waiting long.

249
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,039
What would you like to eat?

250
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:35,159
Oh, no need.

251
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:37,679
Ms. Bai,

252
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,000
I'm sorry.

253
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,080
Before I could even speak,

254
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,279
Mr. Jiang

255
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:44,440
warned me not to discuss your matters.

256
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,440
I...

257
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,000
It's alright, Miss Gao.

258
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,679
Thank you anyway.

259
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,680
I appreciate the effort.

260
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:54,639
Ms. Bai, you've helped me so much before.

261
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,759
And you even helped arrange

262
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:58,279
for my son's schooling.

263
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,000
It's nothing,

264
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:01,360
so no need to thank me.

265
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,320
It's a pity.

266
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:07,240
Mr. Jiang doesn't trust me now.

267
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,960
In the future, I won't be able
to keep helping you, Miss Gao.

268
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:25,390
Someone delivered this
to Mr. Jiang early this morning.

269
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,759
I made a copy.

270
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,000
Maybe

271
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:31,240
this is an opportunity for you, Ms. Bai.

272
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:48,679
Why did you want to see me, Mr. Jiang?

273
00:13:57,940 --> 00:14:00,260
(Lysen Group & Bosi Real Estate
Linwei Alley Urban Renewal Project Collaboration Proposal)

274
00:14:08,060 --> 00:14:11,620
(Linwei Alley Area
Detailed Regulatory Planning Map)

275
00:14:27,879 --> 00:14:28,799
I thought you

276
00:14:28,799 --> 00:14:30,480
weren't interested in real estate.

277
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:31,840
I'm not.

278
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,519
But I am interested
in acquiring companies.

279
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:37,759
I want to acquire this Bosi Real Estate.

280
00:14:41,399 --> 00:14:42,200
Yuci,

281
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,120
I've always owed you a "thank you."

282
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:47,960
You helped me save

283
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,919
Lysen's stock price

284
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:50,360
