285
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,919
on the Dada Wine Industry project.

286
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:55,000
I really like the way you do things.

287
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,399
You're decisive,

288
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:00,390
and you have a good head
on your shoulders.

289
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,960
Lysen needs people like you.

290
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:07,039
I'll give you a chance.

291
00:15:08,039 --> 00:15:09,559
If this gets done,

292
00:15:10,039 --> 00:15:11,519
you can take your pick

293
00:15:11,519 --> 00:15:12,600
of being the head

294
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,279
of Investment Dept 1, 2, or 3.

295
00:15:34,639 --> 00:15:35,919
Mr. Li, I'm here.

296
00:15:37,039 --> 00:15:37,840
Have a seat.

297
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,279
Unfortunately,

298
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,320
