a cup of tea here again, right?

302
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,879
The matter with Young Master Jiang

303
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,440
was Liu Yang's failure.

304
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,120
I, however, held on

305
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,399
