306
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:14,679
No one understands
Jiang Dongchao better than I do.

307
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,639
I know what he wants next.

308
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:19,480
Mr. Jiang has always
wanted to acquire Bosi.

309
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,240
So he is determined to get
that land in Linwei Alley

310
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:23,799
that Bosi has their eye on.

311
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:28,200
As long as you

312
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,559
can let me return to Lysen,

313
00:16:29,639 --> 00:16:30,480
I'll have a way...

314
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,200
Ms. Bai.

315
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,120
The process doesn't matter to me at all.

316
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,879
You know exactly what my goal is.

317
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,720
I want Jiang Dongchao to leave Lysen.

318
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,039
If you have the ability,

319
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:43,320
use your own strength

320
00:16:43,559 --> 00:16:44,600
to return to Lysen.

321
00:16:44,799 --> 00:16:45,759
Once it's done,

322
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,799
then come and talk terms with me.

323
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,559
Thanks for setting it up

324
00:17:04,559 --> 00:17:06,160
