325
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,920
Congratulations on
getting your wish, Mr. Han.

326
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,790
Tell me, is there
anything I can do for you?

327
00:17:15,810 --> 00:17:16,759
Help me investigate

328
