between these two people.

329
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:25,039
Bai Liangliang
is one of yours from Lysen.

330
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,599
As for this Xian Pengyu,

331
00:17:28,070 --> 00:17:29,400
