on Zhaohui Private Equity.

334
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,839
Hello, Mr. Pengyu.

335
00:17:42,839 --> 00:17:43,640
Hello.

336
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,440
I'm Han Congfei.

337
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,990
I've read all the articles
you've written on your public account.

338
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,559
Judging by your writing style,

339
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,759
I thought you were some old man.

340
00:17:58,519 --> 00:17:59,640
So, what do

341
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,839
