348
00:18:12,839 --> 00:18:14,400
If I could land an interview with you,

349
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,599
it would be my honor.

350
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,200
Let's skip the pleasantries.

351
00:18:17,519 --> 00:18:18,640
Who doesn't know

352
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:21,119
