353
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:23,160
I only like two things.

354
00:18:23,559 --> 00:18:25,400
Drinking and making friends.

355
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,799
Whoever drinks with me

356
00:18:32,279 --> 00:18:34,559
