at Yuanjian Club keeping an eye on him.

359
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:44,440
(Yuanjian)

360
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,240
Let's talk.

361
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,400
What are your instructions?

362
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:47,480
Don't you know

363
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,920
