in a commercial building.

382
00:19:32,599 --> 00:19:34,759
And so far, it's been completely vacant.

383
00:19:34,759 --> 00:19:35,880
No external leasing.

384
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,720
This is the info on the building.

385
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:42,620
(Yinyu Commercial Building)

386
