half of Yang Jinwan's heart?

439
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,839
Who is Yang Jinwan?

440
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,400
The helmsman of Bosi Real Estate,

441
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,279
Sir Yang.

442
00:22:17,220 --> 00:22:20,799
