521
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:20,319
Then let her have it.

522
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:22,039
Rao Yuci.

523
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,640
Lysen isn't a place for you
to play games.

524
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,559
If you don't grab

525
00:26:28,559 --> 00:26:29,680
