534
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,440
Boss.

535
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,319
Mr. Yu.

536
00:27:07,319 --> 00:27:08,039
Boss.

537
00:27:08,319 --> 00:27:09,119
Mr. Yu.

538
00:27:09,559 --> 00:27:10,400
Don't worry.

539
00:27:26,359 --> 00:27:27,160
Ms. Bai,

540
00:27:28,839 --> 00:27:30,039
