558
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,480
(No. 88)
Alright, we're here.

559
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,759
Let me do it.

560
00:28:56,759 --> 00:28:57,559
I'll do it.

561
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:58,720
Come.

562
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:00,680
Careful.

563
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:01,680
Okay.

564
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:02,759
Watch out.

565
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,440
Liang...

566
00:29:27,119 --> 00:29:27,920
The dry cleaner guy

567
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:29,600
owed a huge amount of money
and ran away.

568
00:29:29,839 --> 00:29:31,319
It hasn't even been two years,

569
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:33,160
and you want me to move to Linwei Alley

570
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:33,920
to be with him?

571
00:29:34,559 --> 00:29:35,720
What if he runs off too?

572
00:29:36,519 --> 00:29:37,400
Where would we go?

573
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,160
He won't, Liangliang.

574
00:29:39,759 --> 00:29:41,359
Mr. Xu is not that kind of person.

575
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,640
Mr. Xu is a good man.

576
00:29:44,759 --> 00:29:46,079
He's honest and down-to-earth.

577
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:48,480
And he is sincerely kind

578
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:50,119
to two of us.

579
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,640
In my heart,

580
00:29:53,119 --> 00:29:54,480
I have already accepted him.

581
00:29:56,319 --> 00:29:57,759
Meeting Mr. Xu

582
00:29:59,559 --> 00:30:00,880
is my good fortune.

583
00:30:01,359 --> 00:30:02,799
He's your good fortune,

584
00:30:03,279 --> 00:30:04,319
not mine.

585
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,400
Mr. Xu

586
00:30:07,759 --> 00:30:09,799
doesn't just...

587
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:11,039
He doesn't just talk

588
00:30:11,039 --> 00:30:12,000
about being good to us.

589
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,960
He actually shows it
through his actions.

590
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,920
He's even prepared your college tuition

591
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,839
and living expenses for you.

592
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,480
I really

593
00:30:20,799 --> 00:30:22,400
hope you can accept him.

594
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:37,200
I am never calling him "Dad."

595
00:30:45,359 --> 00:30:46,160
Fine.

596
00:30:47,319 --> 00:30:48,119
Fine.

597
00:30:52,540 --> 00:30:54,540
(No. 88 Linwei Alley)

598
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,559
You're looking for Mr. Xu

599
00:31:06,559 --> 00:31:07,599
and his family, right?

600
00:31:08,519 --> 00:31:10,580
He went to
the rehabilitation center for treatment.

601
00:31:10,599 --> 00:31:11,559
No one's home.

602
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:13,839
Rehabilitation center?

603
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:15,079
Yes.

604
00:31:18,359 --> 00:31:19,839
You're Liangliang, aren't you?

605
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,559
You have the wrong person.

606
00:32:17,770 --> 00:32:20,240
Do you remember the last time
I walked this road with you?

607
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,200
It was when you first fell ill.

608
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:27,039
I accompanied you to the doctor.

609
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,079
Mr. Xu,

610
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,240
do you still remember me?

611
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:40,359
Liang.

612
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,319
Thank you.

613
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,039
You've been truly good to me,

614
00:32:53,279 --> 00:32:54,960
like a real father.

615
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:57,519
But...

616
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,160
you can't change

617
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:01,079
the thing I want to change most.

618
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:10,340
(Fifteen years ago)

619
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,039
Liangliang.

620
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:16,559
Look.

621
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:17,880
My dad

622
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:19,240
bought this dress for me.

623
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:20,759
But it's a bit big on me.

624
00:33:22,599 --> 00:33:23,559
Why don't you try it on?

625
00:33:24,119 --> 00:33:25,519
This dress was very expensive.

626
00:33:25,519 --> 00:33:26,039
Go try it.

627
00:33:26,039 --> 00:33:27,480
Come on, let's go.

628
00:33:33,559 --> 00:33:34,279
This dress

629
00:33:34,279 --> 00:33:35,759
is like it has your name on it.

630
00:33:36,799 --> 00:33:38,200
How much was it? I'll pay you.

631
00:33:39,119 --> 00:33:39,920
Forget it.

632
00:33:39,930 --> 00:33:41,630
Why talk about money
between best friends?

633
00:33:41,710 --> 00:33:43,680
When my parents return to the country,
I'll treat you to dinner.

634
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:46,200
Xinyi, come down and help me for a bit!

635
00:33:46,319 --> 00:33:47,200
Wait for me.

636
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:10,066
(Yi & Xuan: I want to know if he also waits
every day for us to meet again, just like I do.)

637
00:34:10,067 --> 00:34:12,540
(I hope one day, "I like you"
can be written the other way around.)

638
00:34:18,660 --> 00:34:23,420
(Every intentional turn of the head
is a mask for a racing heart.)

639
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,599
Xinyi,

640
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:34,360
lately, you've been getting quite close

641
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,519
to that Bai Liangliang.

642
00:34:36,199 --> 00:34:36,880
Yeah.

643
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,000
Technically,

644
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:39,400
since you've made a good friend,

645
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:41,159
I should be happy for you.

646
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,480
But sometimes,

647
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:45,119
as someone who's been there,

648
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:47,679
there are things I still need to say.

649
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,199
Mom,

650
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:51,000
what exactly are you trying to say?

651
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:57,280
I just feel like

652
00:34:57,559 --> 00:34:58,880
Bai Liangliang's family background

653
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,519
isn't as good as she claims.

654
00:35:00,519 --> 00:35:01,320
Mom,

655
00:35:02,079 --> 00:35:03,239
what nonsense are you talking?

656
00:35:04,039 --> 00:35:04,880
Keep it down.

657
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,280
You don't know.

658
00:35:06,599 --> 00:35:08,119
From the first time I saw her,

659
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,280
I smelled something

660
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,920
very strange on her.

661
00:35:12,239 --> 00:35:13,320
Like what?

662
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:15,519
Like the smell

663
00:35:15,519 --> 00:35:16,880
of a deli shop.

664
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,239
I can't quite describe it.

665
00:35:18,239 --> 00:35:19,360
You know what I mean.

666
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:23,679
Mom,

667
00:35:24,239 --> 00:35:25,760
could you be overthinking it?

668
00:35:26,559 --> 00:35:27,480
Besides,

669
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,280
I'm not making friends with money.

670
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:31,800
I know.

671
00:35:32,199 --> 00:35:33,880
My daughter, you're the kindest.

672
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:36,679
But if she's lying,

673
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,480
that's a different story.

674
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:41,800
Mom,

675
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:45,679
who would feel comfortable
discussing their family background?

676
00:35:46,119 --> 00:35:46,920
Right?

677
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,639
Besides,

678
00:35:50,639 --> 00:35:51,480
regarding Liangliang,

679
00:35:52,119 --> 00:35:53,559
many classmates already know.

680
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:54,599
Many?

681
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:55,880
What do you mean?

682
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,960
So you know too?

683
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,719
Her family just runs a deli.

684
00:36:00,159 --> 00:36:01,880
And her mother seems

685
00:36:02,519 --> 00:36:04,079
to have been married several times.

686
00:36:04,679 --> 00:36:05,400
See?

687
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,679
Was my guess spot on or what?

688
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,440
What girl doesn't have

689
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,360
a little pride?

690
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,159
Right?

691
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:13,880
So we classmates

692
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,119
have a tacit understanding.

693
00:36:15,599 --> 00:36:16,840
We just don't call her out.

694
00:36:28,639 --> 00:36:30,280
Someone once asked me,

695
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,400
"What is that black dog

696
00:36:33,719 --> 00:36:34,639
in your heart?"

697
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,119
Do you know it yourself?

698
00:36:37,719 --> 00:36:39,039
The black dog in my heart

699
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:45,000
turned out to be a scent.

700
00:36:49,599 --> 00:36:50,400
Liang.

701
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:53,039
I am doing my absolute best

702
00:36:54,039 --> 00:36:55,639
to take from this world

703
00:36:56,039 --> 00:36:57,519
the identity I crave.

704
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,639
On this path,

705
00:37:02,239 --> 00:37:04,199
I don't care what others think of me.

706
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:06,940
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

707
00:37:07,039 --> 00:37:09,580
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

708
00:37:09,599 --> 00:37:12,170
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

709
00:37:12,180 --> 00:37:14,690
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

710
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:18,719
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

711
00:37:18,719 --> 00:37:20,533
(Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan)

712
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:25,920
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

713
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:28,679
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

714
00:37:28,700 --> 00:37:31,239
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.
- Zhang Xinyi likes Li Mingxuan.

715
00:37:31,239 --> 00:37:32,320
Wasn't I right

716
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:34,159
to do that?

717
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,840
Do you think I shouldn't do it?

718
00:37:47,559 --> 00:37:49,440
I spent five years of hard work

719
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:52,159
to climb to the position I'm in now.

720
00:37:52,719 --> 00:37:54,480
I absolutely cannot go in a giant circle

721
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,840
just to end up back at the start.

722
00:38:02,719 --> 00:38:03,880
So today,

723
00:38:04,079 --> 00:38:06,199
I need to ask you for a favor.

724
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,719
Can you promise me?

725
00:38:21,340 --> 00:38:25,000
=Episode 6=
(Black Dog)

726
00:38:25,741 --> 00:38:28,181
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

727
00:38:28,181 --> 00:38:34,381
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

728
00:38:35,141 --> 00:38:38,341
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

729
00:38:38,341 --> 00:38:42,861
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

730
00:38:42,861 --> 00:38:50,381
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

731
00:38:50,381 --> 00:38:54,301
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

732
00:38:54,301 --> 00:38:58,341
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

733
00:38:58,341 --> 00:39:01,861
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

734
00:39:01,861 --> 00:39:05,821
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

735
00:39:05,821 --> 00:39:09,981
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

736
00:39:09,981 --> 00:39:14,181
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

737
00:39:14,181 --> 00:39:17,981
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

738
00:39:17,981 --> 00:39:22,061
♪Keep walking through the light♪

739
00:39:22,061 --> 00:39:26,261
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

740
00:39:26,261 --> 00:39:32,581
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

741
00:39:49,701 --> 00:39:56,341
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

742
00:39:56,341 --> 00:40:00,181
♪An apology that came too late♪

743
00:40:00,181 --> 00:40:04,821
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

744
00:40:04,901 --> 00:40:12,301
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

745
00:40:12,301 --> 00:40:16,381
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

746
00:40:16,381 --> 00:40:20,461
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

747
00:40:20,461 --> 00:40:24,461
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

748
00:40:24,461 --> 00:40:28,221
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

749
00:40:28,221 --> 00:40:32,421
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

750
00:40:32,421 --> 00:40:36,581
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

751
00:40:36,581 --> 00:40:40,301
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

752
00:40:40,301 --> 00:40:44,341
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

753
00:40:44,341 --> 00:40:48,381
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

754
00:40:48,381 --> 00:40:54,581
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
